y of science.','http://philsci-archive.pitt.edu/','http://philsci-archive.pitt.edu/perl/search?_order=bytitle&abstract%2Fkeywords%2Ftitle_srchtype=ALL&_satisfyall=ALL&_action_search=Search&abstract%2Fkeywords%2Ftitle=',NULL,7),(719,147,'Science Books and Films','Science Books and Films is the AAAS review journal for science materials for all ages, including reviews and recommendations for books, videos, software, and web sites.','http://sbfonline.com/','http://sbfonline.com/sample/search.cgi?title_query_type=all&author_query_type&author=&other=&type=B&type=F&type=S&title=',NULL,8),(720,148,'Ingenta','Ingenta restricts access to full text articles. Although access to the full text costs money, the site can be used as a free index.','http://www.ingenta.com/','http://www.ingenta.com/isis/searching/Search/ingenta?database=1&title=',NULL,0),(721,148,'ebrary','Independent researchers who do not have access to ebrary?s databases through their library may now set up an individual account for as little as $5. ebrary Discover spans multiple academic disciplines and provides anytime, anywhere access to over 20,000 authoritative titles including books in full-text, sheet music, reports and other authoritative documents from more than 175 leading publishers such as Cambridge University Press, Random House, Inc., and The McGraw-Hill Companies.','http://www.ebrary.com/company/','http://shop.ebrary.com/Top?layout=search&f00=text&p01=&f01=subject&d=journal&l=en&sch=%A0%A0%A0%A0%A0Search%A0%A0%A0%A0%A0&frm=adv.x&p00=',NULL,1),(722,148,'Questia','Questia provides access to over 47,000 books and 375,000 journal, magazine, and newspaper articles. All books and articles are available in their entirety - search every page. The subscription rate is ranging from 19.05 per month to 119.95 per year.','http://www.questia.com/','http://www.questia.com/SM.qst?act=search&keywordsSearchType=1000&mediaType=book&mediaType=journal&mediaType=magazine&mediaType=newspaper&mediaType=encyclopedia&mediaTyp