earch and other purposes.  The purpose of the Open Video Project is to collect and make available a repository of digitized video content for the digital video, multimedia retrieval, digital library, and other research communities.','http://www.open-video.org/index.php','http://www.open-video.org/results.php?search_field=all&terms=',NULL,0),(735,153,'Access to Australian Government Information and Services','The Australian Government Entry Point offers comprehensive and integrated access to Australian Government information and services.  You will find a concentrated body of Australian Government information through this site. <a href=\"http://www.australia.gov.au\">www.australia.gov.au</a> currently signposts over 700 Australian Government web sites, indexes more than 5,000,000 pages and uses both metadata and full text indexing to ensure it is a comprehensive government portal.','http://www.fed.gov.au','http://govsearch.australia.gov.au/search/search.cgi?collection=gov&form=au&query=&query_phrase=&query_or=&query_not=&meta_f_sand=&scope=&fscope=512&num_ranks=20&chksummary=chksummary&query_and=',NULL,0),(736,153,'Canadian Government Information','Includes links to Canadian government libraries, federal documents and news releases, publications catalogues, and provincial governments. Most information is in English, but some of the linked material is in French, or a combination of French and English.','http://www.nlc-bnc.ca/8/4/index-e.html','http://www.collectionscanada.ca/search/006001-110.01-e.php?q%5B1%5D=pagelevel%3A1&q%5B2%5D=&x=15&y=13&q%5B0%5D=',NULL,1),(737,153,'Directgov','Directgov is a government service giving people access to the latest and widest range of public service information in one place on the Web and on Digital TV. Directgov uses the specifications formulated and consulted on through UK GovTalk.','http://www.direct.gov.uk','http://www.direct.gov.uk/AdvancedSearch/SearchResults/fs/en?NP=1&PO1=C&PI1=W&PF1=A&PG=1&RP=20&SC=__dgov_site&Z=1&PT1=',NU